{"tid":1707809,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"［狗狗家屬請進］如何讓全港的狗狗們得到合適既治療？","createTime":"2019-11-11T11:34:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T16:19:30.000Z","uid":252151,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d4ed2c26323917b5f3ce8d821e33dc7860dde1eb","tid":1707809,"uid":252151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T11:34:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">相信狗狗們既暴力行為升級，狗狗既變態同暴力傾向，家屬有目共睹，精神狀態早已係邊緣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">精神病既徵狀可以包括：</span></span><br />\n脾氣暴燥<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想傷害他人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n妄想被迫害<br />\n訓唔到覺<br />\n幻覺（睇到唔存在既暴徒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，聽到唔存在既聲音）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n繼續比佢地係社會上揸槍揸棍，有機會傷害到他人！我絕不縱容此等暴徒！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以下為攻略：<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">first step: <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">係屋企比多啲關心狗狗，令佢地都覺得自己有病，例如：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n「我見你近排成日疑心重，係咪怕人害你?依啲係精神病既徵狀黎喎！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n<br />\n「訓得好差係唔係？不如睇下精神科點樣幫你訓好啲！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n<br />\nsecond step:<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">帶佢地一齊去睇精神科醫生！！！<br />\n獸醫要人！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n同醫生講佢地既徵狀，嚴重既徵狀要講得清楚！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n例如<br />\n「係屋企都想打人」<br />\n「出街都帶住警棍係身想攻擊他人」<br />\n「係屋企成日話要槍殺哂啲暴徒」<br />\n「有自殘/自殺傾向」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">依啲係好嚴重既徵狀，一定要講清楚，以免佢地真係做得出，遺禍人間<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">third step:</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">白卡！！醫生證明佢mental state唔fit for work<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n同十萬蚊一個月say byeeeeee<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">進階：<br />\n強制入院，調理下身子先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WNbJpLj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWNbJpLj.png&h=52c43a84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VUARyDF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVUARyDF.png&h=0e8b10c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">家屬們：<br />\n此計只宜<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">智取<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">溫柔</span></span>才是最強大的武器喔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n願天下有病的狗狗得到治療，為世界做一件好事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"737a0dcdd6afc351ffc235aa7cb3faa9136fe788","tid":1707809,"uid":252151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T11:35:51.000Z","msg":"甴近平"},{"pid":"191032edd820b831ceead76b6f274c67eb086826","tid":1707809,"uid"